Program: Omnibus
Title: America and Europe a Loosening the Ties
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jvg
Last Broadcast Date: 29 May 1990
What is behind the slow reaction of the US to the new order in a post cold war Europe? A look at the reexamining of troop levels, arms negotiations and a specific role in Europe for the USA.